    "95fa92c216eef1a1a2ee2be067141d9f68adfcaad7c78d0b9fa2a4cf9e9c2f78": "Don't even think about it, [?]! Make one move and I'll slit her throat!",
    "6d5001432e6c388be0472398090de5f4b50b7c17ffebe1a7a7e600eae0c5650a": "We meet again, [?]!",
    "2f243caa552ce88c5156705f0713c6464f165fa7b4a66175f294299cfe395964": "Bah! You win again, [?]! But someday, somehow, I will have my revenge!",
    "59479758fd9b3069e9a9d1802adbfaa95c27f2731f1a98ea8a38a27b7cc5135c": "So you've brought a friend down here to mock me, [?]? Well soon I will be the one mocking you!",
